365
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:33,320
Give me a little.

366
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:35,280
When I make money,
I'll buy you a cart of pears.

367
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:37,040
No.

368
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,680
Sis,

369
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:45,320
