419
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:51,440
(Everything's been made
by the Astronomical Bureau.)

420
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,000
(Inventions don't work.)

421
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,680
(I can still do business.)

422
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:03,880
