(I give up.)

443
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:46,280
(There are millions of words
in a novel.)

444
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:48,000
(I'd have to write it with a brush.)

445
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,600
(It's not realistic.)

446
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:52,540
(And I can't even remember the content.)

