00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,940
(Changle County Government)

455
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:22,540
(Open and Righteous)

456
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,880
Changle County's
Speed Xu Qi'an.

457
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:34,200
Fine.

458
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,920
