00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:42,680
Ningyan,

481
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:43,840
you don't know.

482
00:21:43,860 --> 00:21:45,400
In the few days you've been in prison,

483
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,240
