494
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,600
I'll plead with the Governor.

495
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:07,960
No matter what,

496
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:09,880
I'll make sure you stay.

497
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:11,900
