505
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:38,480
It's just a job.

506
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,320
Let's just slack

507
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:40,520
and relax a bit.

508
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:41,600
Let's relax.

509
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:48,120
It's good to slack.

510
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:51,720
Ningyan,

511
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,680
