554
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,040
Mrs. Zhang,

555
00:24:59,050 --> 00:25:00,810
(Mrs. Zhang, Zhang Yourui's wife)
you have

556
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:02,920
